column5: Can anyone give me some insight on where to look for the Walleye's on Lac Simard , we are heading up in a couple of weeks.
How did you make out? Did you hit the shouls by gull island? The north end of bryson island is pretty fruit full in june
Was able to make it up to the lake four times this year, Bryson , Gull, the river all produced nice fish for us.
